rComments: Truth be told, I hated her classes. I took 2 courses with her and she made us read +100 pgs per lecture and rarely gave an actual lecture. So, when time came to study for the exam, I had no idea what to study for. I had notes from our discussions, but how do I know if she's going to put what some random person said in class on the exam? AWFUL!
shes not terrible, just not great.  Not the most approachable person, but nice.  The class discussions need more stimulation, they are horrible. Her tests are fair however, no surprises.
worst prof. ever. doesn't reply emails. doesn't give part marks. and would fail assignments !
